Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.08,0:00:05.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A letter from radio-name Ten-chan:
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.00,0:00:07.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think bullying is a good thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.42,0:00:08.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I agree, Ten-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.25,0:00:09.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bullying is uncool.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.38,0:01:35.76,LEFT,,0000,0000,0000,,Kissing in Love
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.68,0:01:39.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.90,0:01:49.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Umm?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.65,0:01:52.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's 30 minutes before airtime.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.52,0:01:54.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, you're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.40,0:01:56.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where's Ume-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.65,0:01:57.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who knows?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.78,0:02:00.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe he's crying like a wimp in his apartment.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.07,0:02:02.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you know that, why don't you give him a call?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.12,0:02:06.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You aren't very enthusiastic.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.00,0:02:08.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can't you see?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.79,0:02:14.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm only here to witness how this cheap program falls apart like a dying flower.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.01,0:02:16.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm done for.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.97,0:02:20.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My career is falling apart like a bowl made out of sand.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.84,0:02:24.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How could I tell Mom or Katsumi about this?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.18,0:02:27.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I should never have participated in such a program.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.02,0:02:29.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's no use crying!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.73,0:02:31.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go on the air!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.15,0:02:35.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Izumi-san, what about the CDs?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.24,0:02:39.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where are the CDs?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.36,0:02:40.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't get them ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.95,0:02:42.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you here then?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.57,0:02:45.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because I haven't found a new job yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.49,0:02:48.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A henchman's struggle, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.37,0:02:50.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like you can do anything by yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.63,0:03:00.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not my fault!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.63,0:03:03.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've submitted my report to the manager.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.22,0:03:04.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I beg you, please at least reassign me somewhere else.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.10,0:03:08.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no, it's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.39,0:03:11.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me get him, but would you keep that a secret?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.56,0:03:13.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Matsu-san, it's Isozaki-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.86,0:03:15.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,From public relations?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.15,0:03:16.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's saying to hurry your ass up.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.86,0:03:18.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.61,0:03:21.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you want, Isozaki?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.65,0:03:22.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm rotten?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.28,0:03:22.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.45,0:03:26.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you call just to mock me?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.58,0:03:33.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's so mean.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.96,0:03:35.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good going, Isozaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.96,0:03:37.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's 10 years worth of public relations.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.42,0:03:41.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're so different drom the wimp I just kicked.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.55,0:03:43.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's have lunch some day.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.30,0:03:44.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's on me, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.39,0:03:48.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Roll that deal along. Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.68,0:03:52.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Finally, luck is coming my way.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.02,0:03:58.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's up, Massan?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.28,0:04:00.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.04,0:04:10.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.08,0:04:14.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I brought the requested CD's from the library.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.71,0:04:17.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks Maico, for even covering for the A.D.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.63,0:04:20.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was asked by Masudamasu-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.13,0:04:22.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.47,0:04:24.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't disobey your master, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.14,0:04:29.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Since you're so honest, I'll give you a special prize today.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.35,0:04:31.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll put you in charge of today's program.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.64,0:04:33.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do as you like.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.18,0:04:34.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.69,0:04:35.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.90,0:04:37.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I doubt you can do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.44,0:04:38.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,OK!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.44,0:04:40.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll try, try, and try hard!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.65,0:04:41.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.57,0:04:45.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't accept so easily.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.61,0:04:47.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ume-san isn't here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.99,0:04:49.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Izumi-san isn't cooperative either.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.62,0:04:52.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nobody is doing anything for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.46,0:04:55.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All we have is Suga-san's script.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.83,0:04:58.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way we can go on the air like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.42,0:04:59.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.92,0:05:03.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you have no intention of going on the air, Densuke-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.51,0:05:09.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of cource I do!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.35,0:05:11.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I'm here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.27,0:05:13.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then let's do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.18,0:05:15.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do it? Me?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.52,0:05:16.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.49,0:05:25.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fine. I'll do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.20,0:05:30.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll make the listeners say that it was better that ever.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.33,0:05:33.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Densuke-kun, you're shining!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.37,0:05:35.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's so not good!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.21,0:05:36.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no other way!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.87,0:05:39.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's impossible with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.17,0:05:40.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm still doing it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.75,0:05:42.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Have fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.00,0:05:44.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}A no-good A.D.'s direction, huh?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.59,0:05:46.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This should be quite a show.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.76,0:05:53.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, the special death metal CD by our guest from 2 weeks ago...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.06,0:05:58.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,goes out to pen-name.... from Tokyo.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.68,0:05:57.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dang!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.69,0:06:00.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, again...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.11,0:06:01.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nice! You're shining!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.95,0:06:11.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't this a bit too harsh for training?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.53,0:06:13.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A hard lesson is needed from time to time.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.20,0:06:16.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.08,0:06:20.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hard lessons are needed.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.63,0:06:28.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Director Densuke-san, the chief, Masudamasu-san, is here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.80,0:06:30.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Would you work hard and show how good you are?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.72,0:06:31.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.43,0:06:32.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,120,121...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.76,0:06:35.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Keep on going!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.06,0:06:36.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.06,0:06:39.23,COMME,,0000,0000,0000,,After the commercial, we'll go to our usual corner.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.64,0:06:37.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, how scary.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.23,0:06:40.39,COMME,,0000,0000,0000,,Stay tuned.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.73,0:06:44.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A street interview!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.40,0:06:52.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We've already messed up 123 times after just the first corner.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.70,0:06:55.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's beautiful mathematically, but, man, that's not the point!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.58,0:06:59.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Densuke-san, please relax.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.04,0:07:02.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You just have to run it according to the cue sheet.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.21,0:07:07.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will finish the talk as directed,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.21,0:07:10.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so you just have to properly run the tapes and songs...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.05,0:07:14.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me that! You're a robot!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.93,0:07:16.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And I'm only a human!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.64,0:07:17.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't help but make mistakes!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.39,0:07:19.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And now you're whining.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.44,0:07:25.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Densuke-san, everyone makes mistakes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.57,0:07:29.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But you should be able to put forth an effort so you don't make mistakes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.69,0:07:30.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's keep trying.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.11,0:07:32.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.95,0:07:34.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And I am trying.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.04,0:07:38.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, the commercial is over.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.21,0:07:46.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.67,0:07:49.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please pardon our mistakes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.92,0:07:54.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now I would like to get started with our usual corner.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.26,0:07:56.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,OK, the CD...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.26,0:07:56.43,COMME,,0000,0000,0000,,Maico's That's Nice!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.55,0:07:59.81,COMME,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll take letters from the listeners,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.81,0:08:05.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and we'll see what you want to say, or what you want me to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.52,0:08:01.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.14,0:08:05.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why is this CD here?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.61,0:08:11.40,COMME,,0000,0000,0000,,Try whatever you want to make my CPU overheat by putting me in a bind.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.07,0:08:10.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How dirty of you to play it like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.99,0:08:13.74,COMME,,0000,0000,0000,,The first one is a request.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.78,0:08:17.45,COMME,,0000,0000,0000,,Requesting Sato Machiko-san's "Kissing in Love".
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.45,0:08:17.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait a sec, Izumi-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.91,0:08:21.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I played this in the Oldies Special once before.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.08,0:08:19.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where are you...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.16,0:08:24.25,COMME,,0000,0000,0000,,This time, the letter is from Los Angeles.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.84,0:08:31.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.38,0:08:34.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A staff member just came in.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.51,0:08:35.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We are still on the air.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.68,0:08:38.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm asking you, why are you putting this song on?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.47,0:08:40.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's a huge accident.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.97,0:08:42.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We are on the air.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.77,0:08:48.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As an android personality, I must continue the broadcast.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.11,0:08:51.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The requester from Los Angeles is...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.78,0:08:59.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This letter...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.91,0:09:01.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you want me to do it again?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.50,0:09:09.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This letter is from the popular producer, Takatou Kenzi-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.59,0:09:11.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good evening, Maico-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.88,0:09:13.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, good evening.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.55,0:09:18.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The song I request, "Kissing in Love", is the first song I produced.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.14,0:09:18.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.30,0:09:19.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What right do you have to do this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.22,0:09:22.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When I heard her sing in the studio,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.97,0:09:27.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was confident that she was once-in-a-decade material.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.56,0:09:30.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I still believe that, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.57,0:09:31.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.15,0:09:38.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But the office I belonged to demanded I start promoting her as soon as possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.62,0:09:40.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They didn't care if she only lasted for a short time.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.95,0:09:43.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I resisted as much as possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.24,0:09:47.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She might be talented, but she was still immature as a singer.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.29,0:09:50.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So I had to nurture her, take time.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.63,0:09:52.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I really believed that.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.00,0:09:59.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I ended up almost being chased out of the position as the producer for Sato Machiko-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.35,0:10:07.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After that, I tried to contact her several times, but I have never seen her since.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.06,0:10:12.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I still think about her every time I hear "Kissing in Love".
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.52,0:10:15.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The other day, someone from Japan Broadcasting told me that
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.32,0:10:20.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sato Machiko-san is working as a stuff member on your program.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.49,0:10:23.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To Sato Machiko-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.03,0:10:27.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,no, to Izumi, I want to say, "I want to see you again."
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.00,0:10:30.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"And I want to dedicate this song to her one more time."
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.17,0:10:33.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's the letter.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.55,0:10:36.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is a song Takatou Kenzi-san is dedicating to Izumi-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.51,0:10:37.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Enjoy.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.01,0:10:40.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sato Machiko-san's "Kissing in Love".
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.93,0:10:42.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The CD!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.10,0:10:49.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's so incredible, Maico-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.73,0:10:51.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Matsu-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.77,0:10:54.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is why you're scum.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.57,0:10:57.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who would turn down the volume during such a good scene?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.82,0:11:04.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Izumi-san, a program that allows me to lie doesn't exist within me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.53,0:11:07.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can only act honestly.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.54,0:11:11.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, when I read this, I wanted to tell, on the air...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.71,0:11:16.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All the listeners, and you, Izumi-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.34,0:11:19.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You could have spoken with me directly!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.34,0:11:22.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But this is a letter intended for this program.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.64,0:11:26.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What an inflexible android, really.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.93,0:11:29.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So embarrassing.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.73,0:11:33.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've always thought I was betrayed.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.44,0:11:36.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've always hated him.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.78,0:11:39.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Were you listening?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.11,0:11:42.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, then we don't need to explain.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.99,0:11:45.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the spot for the seasoned mixer.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.45,0:11:46.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go for it, Ume-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.05,0:12:01.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sato Machiko-san, please take this letter.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.66,0:12:26.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's so shining.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.00,0:14:08.05,LEFT,,0000,0000,0000,,Maico's Diary
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.34,0:14:03.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is elite public relations officer, Kacchin.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.17,0:14:06.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The other day, I went to play a survival game with friends from my college days.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.05,0:14:24.94,COMME,,0000,0000,0000,,I was very happy to get a letter from overseas. Izumi-san was very happy too. But something is strange. The illumination settings haven't changed, but the studio seems brighter.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.05,0:14:09.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm good sniper,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.34,0:14:13.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so I hid behind some object, and was waiting for them to move.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.06,0:14:15.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But nobody came around even after 3 days.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.14,0:14:17.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought my plan was perfect!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.39,0:14:20.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And it was so mean that they all left for somewhere else!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.65,0:14:23.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next Android Ana Maico 2010
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.65,0:14:24.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You are so meek.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.15,0:14:27.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,People tell me that all the time too.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.15,0:14:30.49,LEFT,,0000,0000,0000,,You are so meek
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.49,0:14:29.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That you're so honest with yourself.
